headline: DSG Appoints Elizabeth Ubell to Board of Directors
summary: Veteran Demand Generation Executive Joins Award-Winning Board Amid Industry Transformation Elizabeth Ubell, Chief Commercial Officer, Sysco International DSG is pleased to announce the appointment of Elizabeth Ubell to its Board of Directors.
